citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on 27-APR
- 22. There was no answer at the door of the residence. Called the licensee and they were away from the facility and
unable to return to complete the inspection.
End Section
